item.title: 【Cinema Center】CLIP - GRACHI | First 14 minutes of the TV movie “Quiero Mis 16”/“Matilda’s Sweet 16” in HD (Latin American Spanish Audio) (Nickelodeon)
item.description:
“Quiero Mis 16, Matilda” (known as “Matilda’s Sweet 16” in Canada, U.K., Africa and Asia) it’s Nickelodeon’s Grachi first TV movie, it was premiered on August 25, 2011 trough Nickelodeon Latin America (excepting Brazil) 3 months after Season 1 ended. And later was dubbed and broadcasted worldwide, and released on DVD.

This is also the first movie ever produced by Nickelodeon Latin America. It is based on a popular MTV series called “My Super Sweet 16”

LANGUAGE: Latin American Spanish (Original recording)
ASPECT: HD 720p
